AUTODODGE: Toggle automatic dodging in combat

Syntax: autododge [on|off]

DESCRIPTION:
  Toggles automatic dodging. When enabled, your character will attempt to
  dodge incoming attacks each round. Dodging costs 1 APM per dodge attempt.

  Dodge bonus is based on Physical Prowess (PP): +1 per PP above 10.

  autododge    : toggles on/off
  autododge on : enables auto-dodge
  autododge off: disables auto-dodge

SEE ALSO: autoparry, dodge, parry, combat
